Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.30,Faqi,,0,0,0,,OK, Boss.{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}遵命 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,悠久的凍土啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.72,Default1,,0,0,0,,以冰晶的棺柩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,賦予永恆的長眠吧
